Title: Armenian Caritas
URL: https://caritas.am

Armenian Caritas is headquartered in Gyumri.
The organization has about 200 employees and about 80 volunteers. Armenian Caritas operates in the provinces of Shirak, Lori, Gegharkunik, Ararat as well as in the capital, Yerevan. After more than two decades of operation, Armenian Caritas has made positive changes to the lives of thousands of people by implementing countless social and developmental initiatives in 125 communities across Armenia. Today, there are about 50 different programs in place.
